comments:
I got this trying to view the type hierarchy of java.io.FilenameFilter (using F4
key). Ctrl+T just shows a blank hierarchy.

It's seems to originate from some strangeness in a Crystal reports (obfuscated)
jar on my project build path. I will investigate this further and add more detail.

It seems like infinite recursion so it would be nice to add detection of this
situation.
